{"tid":6242,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[HBO科幻重頭劇］ Westworld劇情討論區","createTime":"2016-11-27T09:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T04:58:21.000Z","uid":18286,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb37ce922d7abbdffa87bf1b3bee9b6b54e86fc","tid":6242,"uid":18286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/01/201237_3e621003288293e799337487ca62d51c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F01%2F201237_3e621003288293e799337487ca62d51c.jpg&h=77973339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇集由Jonathan Nolan及Lisa Joy創作及改編，並由二人跟 J.J. Abrams 監製。 <br />\n演員陣容包括《沉默的羔羊》Anthony Hopkins、《地心引力》Ed Harris、《選戰風雲》Evan Rachel Wood、《X-men》James Marsden等人主演。 <br />\n<br />\n《西部世界》（Westworld），劇集根據1973年的同名科幻電影改編。在遙遠的未來， <br />\n一座巨型高科技成人樂園建成，其中包括西部世界，羅馬世界，中世紀世界三大主題版塊的機器人世界。 <br />\n故事開首主要講述這個高科技的主題樂園可以讓人重返大西部世界，居民皆為仿真機器人，讓遊客盡情地享受無盡的殺戮與性愛慾望。被人類為所欲為蹂躪的機器人們，在人工智慧的演化下逐漸產生自我意識， <br />\n對他們的「造物主」展開反撲！ <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.blackcoffeeseries.com/2016/08/news-hbo-westworld-full-trailer.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blackcoffeeseries.com%2F2016%2F08%2Fnews-hbo-westworld-full-trailer.html&d=KsbvExuy2%2Fr%2BCkaPNyjUDMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=2451ba57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.blackcoffeeseries.com/2016/08/news-hbo-westworld-full-trailer.html</a><br />\n<br />\n(如果再有盲西問邊度有得睇，請叫佢死返去第一頁搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\nSeed: <a href=\"https://rarbg.to/torrents.php?search=westworld\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frarbg.to%2Ftorrents.php%3Fsearch%3Dwestworld&d=KsbvExuy2%2Fr%2BCkaPNyjUDMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=bb7a4ae6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rarbg.to/torrents.php?search=westworld</a> <br />\n線上: <a href=\"http://vmus.co/westworld/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%